x=linspace(-2,pi);
[m,l]=size(x);
y=zeros(1,l);
[m,n]=size(x);
for i=1:n
if (0<=x(i) && x(i)<=pi)
y(i)=2-cos(x(i));
elseif(-2<x(i) && x(i)<0)
y(i)=log(x(i)+exp(1));
end
end
plot(x,y)
grid on
title("Gr√°fica de funci√≥n f(x)") % T√≠tulo
